## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most recent changes in public opinion or legal frameworks. Additionally, the sources used may have inherent biases based on their organizational missions or geographic focus. Further research could include more diverse perspectives and updated data to provide a more comprehensive analysis.